{"tid":2391852,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"A酸進度 多圖 你問我未必答","createTime":"2021-02-02T12:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T00:08:12.000Z","uid":223653,"like":66,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"36686b5617fbd16455940bbc7efe41164e410957","tid":2391852,"uid":223653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"我係2020年9月頭食A酸 直到呢家 2021 2月<br />\n大約食多1個月就完<br />\n食A酸有副作用係情況會惡化後再改善<br />\n睇返圖我諗我就係呢種情況<br />\n幸好甩頭髮果d副作用無我份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CBuvGyz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCBuvGyz.jpg&h=023fc849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTotal 洗左大約 $13000 (最一開始果張單整唔見左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XfnxarK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXfnxarK.jpg&h=feff32f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過程時間  9月頭-2月尾 大約7個月<br />\n下面入正題<br />\n未食飯唔好入黎 未食飯唔好入黎<br />\n未食飯唔好入黎 未食飯唔好入黎<br />\n未食飯唔好入黎 未食飯唔好入黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------我是正題線------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9月頭 30mg/day<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/deGaGgF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdeGaGgF.jpg&h=ad24f1fe&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cvbqu90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvbqu90.jpg&h=9e8dd127&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n9月中 30mg/day<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lng2xoS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLng2xoS.jpg&h=5bc60c8c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imgeovx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fimgeovx.jpg&h=9f43aeeb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n9月尾 30mg/day 9月中至尾 情況開始轉好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8dwqKa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8dwqKa.jpg&h=89f014f5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zh3DQaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzh3DQaQ.jpg&h=b872d165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食左一個月就驗肝  結果無事就轉左40mg/day<br />\n10月頭 40mg/day  睇返相10月頭既情況感覺係開始惡化返<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuGucrT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuGucrT.jpg&h=d0b4641a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10月尾 40mg/day<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y9PPcrT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy9PPcrT.jpg&h=e047312e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EboXmkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEboXmkd.jpg&h=c83eb3b1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n11月中 40mg/day  直到11月中又開始好返<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxowqNw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxowqNw.jpg&h=4d6e1705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPNEzFR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPNEzFR.jpg&h=218cb167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n11月尾 50mg/day  <br />\n複診果陣醫生問我40mg頂唔頂得住 我話ok  跟住上50mg/day<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v0gmN00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0gmN00.jpg&h=ac6f5b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fbsk3zk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbsk3zk.jpg&h=c983e96f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dv8PWUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDv8PWUk.jpg&h=93add750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWtz700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWtz700.jpg&h=b1779d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n12月頭 50mg/day   <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLgFi9s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLgFi9s.jpg&h=e91ec17c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GRnJgV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGRnJgV7.jpg&h=50e3e83f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1月頭 60mg/day <br />\n複診醫生再問我50mg頂唔頂得住 我話ok  跟住上60mg/day<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzAiQgt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzAiQgt.jpg&h=61648aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQDTD9O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQDTD9O.jpg&h=c1342ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nDcUoBt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnDcUoBt.jpg&h=c17bb1c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2月頭 60mg/day  即係現在  比一開始好左好多啦~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kAEvGoH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkAEvGoH.jpg&h=4dd39b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhezoB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhezoB2.jpg&h=032930bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aN4SUJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaN4SUJH.jpg&h=1b8dec0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我既Total 口服A酸劑量佢講過個數比我聽  食夠就要停<br />\n但我唔記得左個數同點計<br />\n所以我上網search左   好似係  120mg ~ 150mg  x  體重 = Total 口服A酸劑量<br />\n我自己就食埋呢個2月就要停<br />\n最後佢仲比左2盒 溫和A酸 比我停食A酸之後搽臉用<br />\n<br />\n希望會再好d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e8aa76ed968ebd926f7680e319c397a97a330d","tid":2391852,"uid":26354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:43:12.000Z","msg":"幾型"},{"pid":"9a550e379065c5c415f9d6ca4254f6d8a30a427b","tid":2391852,"uid":248270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"尾三張圖d頭髮好似少左"},{"pid":"54085bb0fa1a2b1dfa11044ba7c3244c04554650","tid":2391852,"uid":373762,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ObUvGDF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FObUvGDF.gif&h=e74b2996&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"525f11755b892921b732329686ee3c1a016a0f45","tid":2391852,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:47:58.000Z","msg":"幸好甩頭髮果d副作用無我份<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但明顯少左頭髮喎"},{"pid":"b7e1c9df156a25cb00761a1802c4ecbcbbe031fd","tid":2391852,"uid":83998,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"唔Blur下自己個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十分同意醫暗瘡只有A酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1dd013f550d8ea81d937e32ed1ce18acc1b38a7","tid":2391852,"uid":223653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"525f11755b892921b732329686ee3c1a016a0f45","tid":2391852,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:47:58.000Z","msg":"幸好甩頭髮果d副作用無我份<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但明顯少左頭髮喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"可能係...................<br />\n角度問題姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536bc43182eb4dd6cac4b86f6a0c0e4f1b40ca59","tid":2391852,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:53:17.000Z","msg":"我食緊就第四個月仲有爆"},{"pid":"8352a07b02fdd1f9b85d2092de